<div id="review_45423879" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/45423879" />
    <a title="Jeff M" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/925601-jeff-m"><img alt="Jeff M" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_50x66-82093808bca726cb3249a493fbd3bd0f.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/45423879?book_show_action=true">Feb 04, 2009</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jeff M" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jeff M" href="/user/show/925601-jeff-m">Jeff M</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer45423879" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1233270273611371194">While I do like Voltaire&apos;s writings, I would have to recommend Candide over this one. Just not as witty or tongue and cheek as his other writings. Sort of a typical hero/fantasy story. Though Voltaire&apos;s style and imagination make it readable, the story is rather cliche, and sadly it was probably cliche even before the time of Voltaire.</span>
  <span id="freeText1233270273611371194" style="display:none">While I do like Voltaire's writings, I would have to recommend Candide over this one. Just not as witty or tongue and cheek as his other writings. Sort of a typical hero/fantasy story. Though Voltaire's style and imagination make it readable, the story is rather cliche, and sadly it was probably cliche even before the time of Voltaire.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1233270273611371194" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


