        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3191069635" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7626130530916656974">“It was agreed, on all hands, that the affairs of this world took sometimes a quite different turn from what the wisest patriots would wish them. The Hermit replied, the ways of Providence are often very intricate and obscure, and men were much to blame for casting reflections on the conduct of the whole, upon the bare inspection of the minutest part.”</span>

          </span>
